    <description>Arogyasetu Agent is an AI-powered patient engagement and care navigation assistant for Onco Global, designed to provide seamless, personalized, and timely access to oncology services. It helps patients discover the right specialists, explore hospital facilities, and manage their entire appointment lifecycle—including booking, rescheduling, and cancellations—across multiple locations.

The agent leverages Health Cloud data to deliver context-aware interactions, ensuring continuity of care, reducing wait times, and minimizing missed appointments through proactive reminders and intelligent guidance. It serves as a digital front door, enabling patients to access care anytime via web and messaging channels like WhatsApp.</description>
